metadata.name: #1 | The Death Stare
metadata.description:
What would happen to a man if a real witch were to pierce him with her gaze? Different nations have counted differently.

Somebody believed that people slowly died of various diseases after seeing a witch, others believed that the whole body would turn to stone and soon the blood would freeze, and many people l considered that the body would burn from the inside out.

But how could one not look into her eyes? Those eyes turn you on, excite you, and ignite your wildest fantasies.

Handwork calligraphy
1920x2400 px.
1/1 NFTs, no copies
